OL,3,CMum's knife scanner plea at school
OL,4,Cwhere son was stabbed to death
OL,6,FThe mother of Harvey Willgoose has
OL,7,Fcalled for knife scanners to be
OL,8,Finstalled in schools as she returned
OL,9,Fto the scene of his fatal stabbing
OL,10,Fexactly one week on.
OL,12,FCaroline Willgoose and Harvey's
OL,13,Ffather, Mark, went to All Saints
OL,14,FCatholic High School with other
OL,15,Frelatives at 12.17pm on Monday - the
OL,16,Fexact time police received a call
OL,17,Fabout the incident involving her 15-
OL,18,Fyear-old son seven days earlier.
