OL,3,CMum's knife scanner plea at school
OL,4,Cwhere son was stabbed to death
OL,6,FHarvey died after being stabbed in the
OL,7,Fchest on 3 February. A 15-year-old
OL,8,Fboy, who cannot be named because of
OL,9,Fhis age, has been charged with murder,
OL,10,Fas well as possession of a bladed
OL,11,Farticle and affray.
OL,13,FMrs Willgoose told ITV News: "I know
OL,14,Fit goes deeper than this but I just
OL,15,Fwant children safe, I want knife
OL,16,Farches in every school.
OL,18,F"I know it's not very nice and every
OL,19,Fbody says it's impossible, but it
OL,20,Fcan't be impossible. You can't even go
OL,21,Fto a museum without being searched."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
