OL,3,CMum's knife scanner plea at school
OL,4,Cwhere son was stabbed to death
OL,6,FIn a video posted on social media, she
OL,7,Fadded: "The one thing I want out of
OL,8,Fthis... I'm urgently saying I want
OL,9,Fknife arches in every school from
OL,10,Ftomorrow, from as soon as we can."
OL,12,FAll Saints was closed for two days
OL,13,Ffollowing Harvey's death.
OL,15,FIn a statement, school leaders
OL,16,Fdescribed it as "a tragic and shocking
OL,17,Fincident" which "shakes us to our
OL,18,Fcore".
