OL,3,CMum's knife scanner plea at school
OL,4,Cwhere son was stabbed to death
OL,6,FSteve Davies, chief executive of the
OL,7,FSt Clare Catholic Multi Academy Trust
OL,8,Fwhich runs the school, said: "All
OL,9,FSaints has always been proud of the
OL,10,Fwarmth, care and love that the school
OL,11,Fis known for. We will all need to draw
OL,12,Fon those qualities in rebuilding
OL,13,Fconfidence."
OL,15,FHe called on people not to speculate
OL,16,Fabout the incident.
