OL,3,CMum's knife scanner plea at school
OL,4,Cwhere son was stabbed to death
OL,6,F"He was a funny kid. People that know
OL,7,Fus and know Harvey know that he was
OL,8,Fjust a crazy kid. He wanted to be
OL,9,Feverybody's friend and he was."
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police declined to
OL,12,Fcomment.
OL,14,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,15,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,16,FLeaders, installing knife arches would
OL,17,Fbe a "knee jerk reaction".
