OL,3,CMum's knife scanner plea at school
OL,4,Cwhere son was stabbed to death
OL,6,FHe said: "What we really need is a
OL,7,Flong term response to this -
OL,8,Finvestment in our communities,
OL,9,Finvestment in long term support for
OL,10,Fyoung people so they don't feel the
OL,11,Fneed to turn to knife crime, so they
OL,12,Fhave alternatives in our communities."
OL,14,FThe Department for Education has been
OL,15,Fcontacted for a response.
